<p>If we become aware of any ongoing concerns or problems concerning our privacy practices, we will take these issues seriously and work to address these concerns. If you have any further queries relating to our privacy policy, or you have a problem or complaint, please contact us at our <a href="https://sherwinwilliams.ethicspointvp.com/custom/sherwinwilliams/web/en/dp/form_data.asp?SourceName=test&amp;SourceURL=">Global Privacy Portal</a>.&nbsp; If you are not satisfied with our handling of your problem or complaint you may make a complaint to the Australian Information Commissioner &ndash; for further details please visit <a href="http://www.oaic.gov.au/">http://www.oaic.gov.au/</a></p>

